title: Day 846
content:
# Day 846

Went dirt-biking today. It feels so badass having a combustion engine rumble beneath you while you haul ass and drive over dirt, rocks, and mud. Idaho and Montana are truly breathtaking, God's country. The day was special, and a fantastic reminder that life is about the journey, not just the destination. But it's nice to know that a great destination awaits.
